 <H1>Where to Implement Adaptivity?</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>In Software: compiler and/or OS
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>(Static) Knowledge of program behavior
<LI>Factored into optimization and scheduling
<LI>Extra code, overhead
<LI>Lack of dynamic run-time information
<LI>Rate of adaptivity
<LI>Requires recompilation, OS changes
</UL></UL></P>
